---
---

<div class="hw-shell">
  <div class="hw-chrome">
    <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span class="hw-label">quipthread</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hw-root">
    <div class="hw-header">
      <h2 class="hw-title">3 Comments</h2>
      <div class="hw-user-bar">
        <span class="hw-av hw-av-lg hw-av-you">SK</span>
        <span class="hw-user-name">Sarah K.</span>
        <button class="hw-btn-ghost">Sign out</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="hw-comment-list">
      <li class="hw-comment">
        <span class="hw-av hw-av-lg hw-av-blue">AM</span>
        <div class="hw-comment-body">
          <div class="hw-comment-meta">
            <span class="hw-author">Alex M.</span>
            <span class="hw-ts">2 hours ago</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hw-content">The new dark mode looks fantastic. Really appreciate the attention to detail on the color transitions.</div>
          <div class="hw-actions">
            <button class="hw-btn-ghost hw-action-btn">Reply</button>
          </div>
          <div class="hw-replies">
            <div class="hw-reply">
              <span class="hw-av hw-av-sm hw-av-you">SK</span>
              <div class="hw-comment-body">
                <div class="hw-comment-meta">
                  <span class="hw-author">Sarah K.</span>
                  <span class="hw-ts">1 hour ago</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hw-content">Thanks! Getting the contrast ratio right was the tricky part.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="hw-comment">
        <span class="hw-av hw-av-lg hw-av-green">JP</span>
        <div class="hw-comment-body">
          <div class="hw-comment-meta">
            <span class="hw-author">Jordan P.</span>
            <span class="hw-ts">yesterday</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hw-content">Switched from Disqus last week. Import worked flawlessly — readers haven't noticed a thing.</div>
          <div class="hw-actions">
            <button class="hw-btn-ghost hw-action-btn">Reply</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="hw-new-comment">
      <div class="hw-new-header">
        <span class="hw-new-label">Leave a comment</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hw-editor-wrapper">
        <div class="hw-toolbar">
          <button class="hw-tb-btn"><strong>B</strong></button>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn"><em>I</em></button>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn"><s>S</s></button>
          <div class="hw-tb-sep"></div>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn">≡</button>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn">№</button>
          <div class="hw-tb-sep"></div>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn">&lt;&gt;</button>
          <button class="hw-tb-btn">↗</button>
        </div>
        <div class="hw-editor-content">
          <p class="hw-placeholder">What are your thoughts?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hw-form-actions">
        <button class="hw-btn-primary">Comment</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .hw-shell {
    --hw-bg:     #0F0F0F;
    --hw-bg-alt: #1A1A1A;
    --hw-text:   #E8E3DC;
    --hw-muted:  #8A8480;
    --hw-border: #2E2E2E;
    --hw-accent: #E07F32;
    --hw-r:      8px;
    --hw-r-sm:   4px;
    --hw-shell-bg:     #161616;
    --hw-shell-border: #2A2A2A;
    --hw-shell-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(212,168,83,0.08), 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    color-scheme: dark;
    background: var(--hw-shell-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--hw-shell-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--hw-shell-shadow);
  }

  :global([data-theme="light"]) .hw-shell {
    --hw-bg:     #f7f4ef;
    --hw-bg-alt: #eeebe4;
    --hw-text:   #1a1714;
    --hw-muted:  #7a7570;
    --hw-border: #d9d4cb;
    --hw-accent: #c06020;
    --hw-shell-bg:     #eeebe4;
    --hw-shell-border: #d9d4cb;
    --hw-shell-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(192,96,32,0.08), 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    color-scheme: light;
  }

  .hw-chrome {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2A2A;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 9px; height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2A2A2A;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .hw-label {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: #8A8480;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .hw-root {
    background: var(--hw-bg);
    color: var(--hw-text);
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .hw-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1.125rem;
  }
  .hw-title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--hw-text);
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  }
  .hw-user-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--hw-muted);
  }
  .hw-user-name { color: var(--hw-text); font-weight: 500; }

  .hw-av {
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--hw-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--hw-border);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--hw-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hw-av-lg  { width: 30px; height: 30px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  .hw-av-sm  { width: 24px; height: 24px; font-size: 0.625rem; }
  .hw-av-you   { background: #1e1610; border-color: rgba(224,127,50,0.3); color: #E07F32; }
  .hw-av-blue  { background: #0f1620; border-color: #1a2535; color: #7eb8e8; }
  .hw-av-green { background: #0d1810; border-color: #162214; color: #6bbd7f; }

  .hw-comment-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }
  .hw-comment { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .hw-comment-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .hw-comment-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .hw-author { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--hw-text); }
  .hw-ts     { font-size: 0.6875rem; color: var(--hw-muted); }
  .hw-content { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--hw-text); line-height: 1.55; }
  .hw-actions { display: flex; margin-top: 0.375rem; }

  .hw-replies {
    margin-top: 0.625rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--hw-border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }
  .hw-reply { display: flex; gap: 0.625rem; }

  .hw-btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--hw-muted);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: var(--hw-r);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .hw-action-btn { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem; }
  .hw-btn-primary {
    background: var(--hw-accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--hw-accent);
    border-radius: var(--hw-r);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .hw-new-comment {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hw-border);
  }
  .hw-new-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .hw-new-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--hw-muted);
  }

  .hw-editor-wrapper {
    border: 1px solid var(--hw-border);
    border-radius: var(--hw-r);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--hw-bg);
  }
  .hw-toolbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hw-border);
    background: var(--hw-bg-alt);
  }
  .hw-tb-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    border-radius: var(--hw-r-sm);
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--hw-muted);
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .hw-tb-sep {
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--hw-border);
    margin: 4px 2px;
    align-self: stretch;
  }
  .hw-editor-content {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.625rem;
    min-height: 52px;
  }
  .hw-placeholder { color: var(--hw-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0; }
  .hw-form-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin-top: 0.625rem;
  }
</style>
